item.title: CVE-2022-4946|2024-08-03T01:55:46.120Z -- unknown -- frontend%20post%20wordpress%20plugin
item.description: The Frontend Post WordPress Plugin WordPress plugin through 2.8.4 does not validate an attribute of one of its shortcode, which could allow users with a role as low as contributor to add a malicious shortcode to a page/post, which will redirect users to an arbitrary domain.
